Patch for design screenshots — apply to run the mobile app without a backend.

To apply:
  cd calendar-ai
  git apply plan/SCREENSHOT-MOCK.patch

To revert after screenshots are done:
  git checkout mobile/src/contexts/AuthContext.tsx
  git checkout mobile/src/screens/HomeScreen.tsx
  git rm mobile/src/services/mockData.ts

---

Trigger words to type in the chat after applying:
  list      → event list
  create    → new event review card
  update    → edit event card
  delete    → select-to-delete list
  conflict  → conflict resolution options
  safety    → safety confirmation gate
  plan      → plan summary with action log
  leisure   → leisure search cards with free-time badges

Screenshots on iOS Simulator: Cmd+S
Screenshots on Android Emulator: camera button in emulator toolbar

